data.description: This 5-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom bi-level home with detached garage in the desirable Redbank Estates offers a welcoming open concept living space with hardwood flooring throughout the main level. As you enter, you're greeted by a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into the dining area and kitchen. The kitchen features a breakfast bar with granite countertops, adding both style and functionality to the space. The main level of the home comprises three generously sized bedrooms and a full bathroom. In addition to the main level, the lower level of this bi-level home offers a versatile space perfect for relaxation and entertainment. Here, you'll find a spacious family room with a wood pellet stove, providing ample room for gatherings. Adjacent to the family room are two additional bedrooms, adding to the total of five bedrooms in the home. These extra bedrooms offer flexibility according to your needs. Furthermore, the lower level features a half bathroom, ensuring convenience and comfort. A standout feature of the lower level is the huge walk-in closet with built-in organizers. Completing the appeal of this wonderful home is its spacious fenced-in backyard. Whether you envision hosting barbecues, gardening, or simply lounging in the sunshine, the spacious backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor living. It's a perfect canvas for creating your own outdoor retreat. This home is conveniently located to Rt.295 for a fast commute to PA or DE, close to shops, restaurants, and River Winds Community Center.
